Class DeviceServiceTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • perfcenter.baseclass.DeviceServiceTime

  • public class DeviceServiceTime
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines service times. This is used by task and virtual resource, and by analytical perfcenter. Service time can be defined as a distribution in the class.
